Title: Work Order: Operation: Shieldwall II
Description:
Once your witchberries are ready to be picked, you'll need only to package them for pick-up.

Just think; your witchberries will be a part of your faction's efforts in Pandaria!
ObjectivesText: Harvest 8 Ripe Witchberry plants and provide 40 Witchberries for Operation: Shieldwall.
